        android:cursorVisible="false"
        android:editable="false"
        android:ems="10"
        android:focusable="false"
        android:focusableInTouchMode="false"
        android:inputType="none"
        android:singleLine="false"
        android:text="The aim is to allow the user a way to escape their pain by creating a harmony between their body and mind. This is done by pairing stimulating visuals with calming sounds. Ideally, the success of this application will lower the risk of children forming a dependence on narcotics. This projectâ€™s success will provide children with severe injuries and trauma a way to manage their pain and discomfort by being fully immersed in an interactive, virtual environment geared specifically to their needs."
